Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:09.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation's going to be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:12.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then school's going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:17.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:20.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I'll get to see everyone in class again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in class...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.38,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooruuun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:24.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Watch it, Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:30.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I didn't win again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You always seem to be surrounded by guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:37.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:40.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It doesn't seem that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:45.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been c-confessed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Confessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:49.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:50.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:53.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:58.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave it to me, saying, "I like this kind of thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Liking candles is pretty unusual, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure... he means the candles?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:49.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:53.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:56.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fireworks festival they hold every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There're lots of night stalls. It's pretty lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Look, it's this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Since summer vacation's about to end,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be nice to go to a festival together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:09.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can all wear yukata, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:13.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fun to do this now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:21.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,what are you doing for the rest of today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:24.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Too hot. Don't wanna move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about we go for karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:36.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke? Sounds good! I love karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, you're a karaoke fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:43.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I like to choose ringtones that I can sing along to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:44.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, what do you like about karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:51.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... for one, the jambalaya at that place is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But the ramen's surprisingly good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, they give you big servings for the parfaits and ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were going to karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:03.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This room's a bit cramped...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm going to order our food and drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:12.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you all like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a melon soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Grapefruit juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, anything to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... iced tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:27.10,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hello? I'd like to place an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they've got the new songs that came out this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.13,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Two iced teas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.11,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,melon soda and grapefruit juice, one each.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll enter the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:36.24,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, a jambalaya and fries, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.03,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.62,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.82,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Take me, summer breeze! Sweep me off my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.89,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Take me, summer breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:01.40,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}This love of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:05.65,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}floats upon the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:10.26,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Catch me, summer breeze! Hold me gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.71,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Touch me, summer breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:16.14,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}A sweet single summer's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:20.16,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}I'll take off with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.89,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}I'll take off with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:34.79,Summer Breeze,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Take me, summer breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, better enter the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:44.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tooru's giving this some serious thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe she's really picky about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she glaring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.36,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,I bravely try to wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:14.14,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm pulled back into a slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:17.03,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,Teary, teary, mumble, mumble,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.47,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to escape from life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:22.26,Ocha Melodical,*,0000,0000,0000,,Caught up in emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.59,Ocha Melodical,*,0000,0000,0000,,I argue with my best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:30.60,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still get in the last word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.25,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's spread this vague magic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.22,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,all across the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:40.83,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,carried by those catchy words!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.46,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,(3, 2, 1, say!)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.34,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocha Melodical Beauty, Bang Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.32,Ocha Melodical,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep smiling along! ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.46,Ocha Melodical,*,0000,0000,0000,,... Glow like a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:05.29,Ocha Melodical,*,0000,0000,0000,,With an appli-tic fortune, wake up the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:48.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:51.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Done with the song book and staring contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:55.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll enter it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:56.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! And, send!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:12.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:17.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:19.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:21.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, the microphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your order!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The jambalaya's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:54.65,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's hot, so please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:54.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the grapefruit juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:58.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The melon soda's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:58.52,A Channel 2,*,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.04,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:04.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess she didn't want to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry I almost made you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:19.96,Koi Hitoya,,0000,0000,0000,,Wounded by the twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:25.35,Koi Hitoya,,0000,0000,0000,,the country girl's maiden heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:31.00,Koi Hitoya,,0000,0000,0000,,This love need never come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:38.99,Koi Hitoya,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me see you, once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of spirit there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just two more songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I sing two more songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can eat eight fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit worrying and just eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you like that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:04.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This one, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:09.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:14.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I've never sung it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:22.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:33.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, it's not on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:45.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:51.22,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, hand in hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:55.46,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,across this great big hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:59.38,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:03.37,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,let's find more fun things to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:15.54,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,A pure white blanket,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:19.45,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,and a giant puppet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.80,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,and a polka-dot skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:27.24,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we can't split them in two to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:31.60,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we fall and want to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.15,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be there for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:39.40,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,When our fast-beating hearts fill up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.07,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be as happy as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:46.29,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, hand in hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:49.86,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,walking straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:54.03,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:58.35,Tomodachi,,0000,0000,0000,,let's find more fun things to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just three more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.25,A Channel 1,*,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know when to give up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's input another song?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then I'll do one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish eating first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the next song will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:19.09,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.16,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:31.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that guy's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The song's so sultry it hurts, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:37.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:39.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:40.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:43.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:45.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:53.26,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon enough, you'll understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:56.47,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,the answer in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:52.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:11:59.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could sing karaoke with Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, come on! One more time, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I was better at singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:37.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, they had a TV show about improving your singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:38.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've worn a yukata to a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bunch of yukata. Which do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This one with the chic color is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember one with that color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:05.37,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's changed color from the mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess my current ones won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe my old ones will fit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those look very adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:29.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're probably Run-chan's mom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:34.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I can break 1*0 cm in those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:42.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be an adult at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:48.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! We put them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the festival, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bright colors are wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You both look spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:07.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But the festival isn't until tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still ten in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We got over-excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:29.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:32.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:33.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, you really do look cute in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:42.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan{\fscx200}-{\r} oh, you curled your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you know... every now and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks won't start for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,so let's check out the stands to kill some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go to a mask stand first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, do you like kids' anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:13.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The stalls from the shopping district always try to give me stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, a candy apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Candy apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, can I have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Tooru, do you want some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, let me have some of your cotton candy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:38.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:46.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan and Nagi-chan are doing the ring toss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I got third place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! A fireworks set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:07.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving fireworks as prizes at a fireworks festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:09.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going for first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:43.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already spent so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:45.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Night stalls are pretty expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:47.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to spend carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Worst case, you end up broke for the second half of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But just looking at things makes you want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:59.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have to deliberately buy things that you can enjoy for longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:04.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy carving?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:09.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, shouldn't we do something we can all enjoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet you've never done candy carving before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:17.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pick an easy one, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:28.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:33.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:49.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:52.17,A Channel 1,*,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't seen all the shops yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.46,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:58.67,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,We will soon begin launching the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:06.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:13.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The crowds...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:14.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know someplace good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,To the top of the hill! There's a secret spot there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, forget about the candy carving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:25.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,My drinking gourd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right at the top of these stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:34.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I don't really care about the fireworks anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:51.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give in, Nagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,All in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A... Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:04.09,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,And that concludes tonight's firework show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:08.33,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,On your way home, please take your trash with you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.82,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,or deposit it in the designated areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:06.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over... already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:11.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:14.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The finale alone just doesn't feel like enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of sad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:17.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:20.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I won some fireworks at the stall earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Nice going, Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:24.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A candle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought those?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:38.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How come there were only sparklers in this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:47.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I kind of like sparklers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:52.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This tastes so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:10.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx200}-{\r} Satou-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now how do I respond to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:20.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't come near me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:23.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,are you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me another {\i1}Nama Sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But look, you're alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said! I am not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:53.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:55.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to the beach, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:00.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch the fireworks again next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:02.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish carving that candy next time, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your priority?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:12.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! It was surprisingly addicting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:17.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:19.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:57.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to the end of August...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:58.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or copying from someone who actually did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:03.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I panicked finishing my picture diary, but I forgot what the weather was like!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:05.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on A-Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.45,0:24:06.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"New Semester"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:08.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's not like we're elementary schoolers...
